data.description: This home has ALL the things plus at a great price point! Including a possible FHA loan assumption at 3.25%    Located in Bullard, with easy access to Tyler.  4 bed, 2.5 bath, open concept, kitchen island, and a shiplap feature wall in the dining area.  The primary bedroom is split from the others with a vaulted ceiling, stunning ensuite complete with a separate soaker tub, and extra large walk in closet. Backyard covered patio looks out to the flat, fenced in backyard.  And there are solar panels to cut down the costs of those electric bills!!! Come see while it's available!
